s]]'' \u2013 \u4e2d\u56fd\u62a5\n\n====Tamil====\n*''[[Makkal Osai]]'' \u2013 {{lang|ta|\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b93\u0b9a\u0bc8}}\n*''[[Malaysia Nanban]]'' \u2013 {{lang|ta|\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0ba8\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bcd}}\n===Ipoh [[terrestrial television|terrestrial channels]]===\nIpoh [[Free-to-air|free-to-air stations]] include:\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n![[Television station]]\n!Channel (via [[MYTV Broadcasting|myFreeview]])\n!Network\n!Broadcast area\n!Broadcast hour\n|-\n| [[TV1 (Malaysia)|TV1 HD]]\n| 101\n| rowspan=2| [[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]\n| rowspan=14| National\n| rowspan=5| [[24/7]]\n|-\n| [[TV2 (Malaysia)|TV2 HD]]\n| 102\n|-\n| [[TV3 (Malaysia)|TV3 HD]]\n| 103\n| rowspan=6| [[Media Prima]]\n|-\n| [[CJ Group|CJ WOW Shop Malay]]\n| 104\n|-\n| [[CJ Group|CJ WOW Shop Chinese]]\n| 106\n|-\n| [[NTV7]]\n| 107\n| rowspan=2| 06:00-02:00 [[Malaysia Standard Time|MST]] (21-Hours)\n|-\n| [[8TV (Malaysia)|8TV]]\n| 108\n|-\n| [[TV9 (Malaysia)|TV9]]\n| 109\n| rowspan=7| [[24/7]]\n|-\n| [[TV Okey|TV Okey HD]]\n| 110\n| rowspan=2| [[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]\n|-\n| [[RTM HD Sports]]\n| 111\n|-\n| [[TV Alhijrah]]\n| 114\n| [[TV Alhijrah|Alhijrah Media]]\n|-\n| [[Astro (television)|Astro GO Shop Malay HD]]\n| 120\n| [[Astro (television)|Astro]]\n|-\n| [[Bernama News Channel]]\n| 121\n| [[Bernama]]\n|-\n| [[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM BES HD]]\n| 123\n| [[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]\n|}\n\n===[[Astro (television)|Astro]] Ipoh===\n====[[Astro (television)|Astro]] Ipoh channels====\n*[[Astro AEC]]\n*[[Astro Arena (TV channel)|Astro Arena]]\n*[[Astro Awani]]\n*[[Astro Ceria]]\n*[[Astro Citra]]\n*[[Astro Hua Hee Dai]]\n*[[Astro Oasis]]\n*[[Astro Prima]]\n*[[Astro Ria]]\n*[[Astro SuperSport]]\n*[[Astro SuperSport|Astro SuperSport 2]]\n*[[Astro SuperSport|Astro SuperSport 3]]\n*[[Astro SuperSport|Astro SuperSport 4]]\n*[[Shuang Xing|Astro Shuang Xing]]\n*[[Astro TVIQ]]\n*[[Astro Vaanavil]]\n*[[Astro Vellit